<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Congratulations on Your Offer for Project Zenith!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Hi,</p>

            <p>We are thrilled to extend this offer to join Project Zenith at ContactTech. We are confident that your skills and experience will make a great impact, and we are excited about the opportunity to work with you.</p>

            <p><strong>However, we need your confirmation as soon as possible to finalize the process.</strong> Please reply to this email with your confirmation at your earliest convenience.</p>

            <p>You only need to simply send "confirmation" to the me:</p>

            <p><strong>Email :</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@contact.com">contact@contact.com</a></p>

            <p>If you have any questions about the Project Zenith or need additional information, please don't hesitate to reach out to us. Your prompt response is greatly appreciated and will help us move forward efficiently.</p>

            <p>Looking forward to hearing from you very soon!</p>

            <p>Best regards,</p>

            <p>Usher</p>
            <p>Senior HR Manager</p>
            <p>ContactTech</p>
        </div>
        <p>&copy; 2022 ContactTech. All rights reserved.</p>
        <div class="email-footer" id="">
            <p>System message: Please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p> <a href="https://www.contact.com/privacy-policy" style="color: #666;">Privacy Policy</a> <a href="https://www.contact.com/terms-of-service" style="color: #666;">Terms of Service</a> </p>
            <p>By following the instructions in this email, you agree to the terms and conditions outlined in our offer letter.</p>
            <p>This is the one of emails you will receive regarding this offer. If you have received any instruction by any other means, please keep it to protect your personal information. </p>
            <p>By Sending "confirmation" to the Usher (contact@contact.com) provided in this email is the only action required to accept the offer. If you have received any other instructions, please contact Usher immediately. </p>
